Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.53,0:00:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起把白祭办起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一起办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就我们5个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走一步是一步了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不清楚结果会怎样…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.37,0:00:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们一定要放声高歌
